title: The Story of a Man Among Men (1984)
description: Synopsis: After getting attacked and almost dying from major head wounds, a lowly gambler (Hiroki Matsukata) swiftly rises in the ranks of the yakuza to lead. With the respect and loyalty of his yakuza family and sworn brothers, he lifts himself as a boss the strongest Yakuza family ever. Along the way he continues to gather the loyalty of quality men as brothers, as the numbers begin to grow in his yakuza army
